data.description: Discover the perfect blend of modern elegance and Southern charm in this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home located in Loranger, Louisiana. Built just 2 years ago, this home is still under builder warranty offering peace of mind and assurance for your investment. A generous sized, 0.26 acre lot gives plenty room to breathe and grow in this well established neighborhood, Wolf Lakes. Flooded with natural light, the spacious living area is ideal for entertaining or relaxing with the family. The sleek kitchen boast stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a separate pantry for ample storage. Enjoy the convenience of a kitchen island with storage and bar seating. The spacious primary bedroom easily accommodates King-sized furniture. It's ensuite offers luxurious double vanity, large soaker tub, separate shower, and 2 expansive walk-in closets. Three additional spacious bedrooms with many possibilities. Enjoy the fenced-in backyard creating privacy and tranquility with a backdrop of local farmland. Enjoy the peaceful evenings with a view of the sunsets and horses grazing across the fence. This Loranger home for sale is conveniently located approximately 11 miles from Amite and 12 miles from Hammond. Call today with any questions and to schedule your appointment.
